T. Husk position relative på parent element når du bruker position: absolute;


CSS fullwidth color bands:
-------------------------
.highlighted::before {
  content: "Note: ";
  position: absolute;
  background: lightgrey;
  z-index: -1;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  right: 0;
  left: 0;
  grid-row: 2 / 3;
}
